Heads up! It's <b>Marissa</b>! <br><br>Many people claim that Lakeview is one of the nicest neighborhoods in Millsberry, filled with the nicest people in Millsberry! Well, if you know Marissa, you know that they aren't kidding! Marissa, a resident of Lakeview since July 09, 2004, may well be the most caring and friendly person you've ever met! That is, if you've met her! <br><br>Marissa is into all things related to animals, so if you're looking to meet someone as alert and intelligent as she, you should start at the zoo! Marissa is always with her animal friends there! Of course, she can also be seen hanging out at the amusement park, the tree house, and even the mall! If you're into spending time with animals or visiting the mall, then you've already got some things in common with Marissa! <br><br>Just what does Marissa buy at the mall, though? Well, she could be buying one of many things! She might be picking up some CDs from the music store&mdash;look for her in the pop, rap, or punk sections! Occasionally, though, the time Marissa spends in the music store isn't spent listening to music? but, rather, singing it! Marissa is in love with both singing and listening to music! <br><br>Many think that Marissa is a very intelligent girl, and why not? She spends most of her free time writing - stories, essays, whatever! She loves to write! </div>
